<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/03/03/friday-tomorrow-march-4-at-the-rubin-museum/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Friday (tomorrow!) March 4 at the Rubin Museum">Friday (tomorrow!) March 4 at the Rubin Museum</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"></p>
<p>I will be talking about Spirals: Fluid Dynamics in Tibetan Art, at the Rubin Museum&#8217;s &#8220;Artists on Art&#8221; series. We&#8217;ll look at a few paintings and a sculpture that have really cool spirally flames and clouds, and swirly water, and I&#8217;ll say intelligent things like, &#8220;Look! Spirals! Aren&#8217;t they neato?&#8221; Details:</p>
<p>Friday March 4, 6:15 pm<br />
Program meets at the base of the spiral staircase.<br />
Rubin Museum of Art<br />
150 W. 17th St.<br />
New York, NY 10011</p>
<p>And it&#8217;s FREE!</p>
<p class="wp-flattr-button">I will be talking about Spirals: Fluid Dynamics in Tibetan Art, at the Rubin Museum&#8217;s &#8220;Artists on Art&#8221; series. We&#8217;ll look at a few paintings and a sculpture
<p>Continue reading <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/03/03/friday-tomorrow-march-4-at-the-rubin-museum/">Friday (tomorrow!) March 4 at the Rubin Museum</a></p>
